  <brief_title>Impact Of Closure Of Patent Foramen Ovale On Apnoea-Hypopnoea-Index, Nocturnal Hypoxemia And Systemic Vascular Function In Patients With Obstructive Sleep Apnoea</brief_title>
  <official_title>Impact Of Closure Of Patent Foramen Ovale On Apnoea-Hypopnoea-Index, Nocturnal Hypoxemia And Systemic Vascular Function In Patients With Obstructive Sleep Apnoea</official_title>
  <sponsors>
